Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't seem that my{\i0}\N{\i1}new role as a Princess{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}equates to all that much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tirek! And I will take what\Nshould've been mine long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With each passing moment, he\Ngrows stronger still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know just the princess\Nwho can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must call in\Nanother to stop Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ho! You're talking\Nabout me I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you girls just\Nlearned so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's something\Ninteresting about the sections
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that Discord bookmarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of you received\Nsomething from the pony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,whose life you helped change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still one key\Nmissing: my element.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Join me, Discord and\Nreclaim your greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Discord has betrayed{\i0}\N{\i1}the ponies of Equestria{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and joined forces with Tirek.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no doubt that Tirek{\i0}\N{\i1}is after Alicorn magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We must rid ourselves\Nof our magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before Tirek has the chance\Nto steal it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subtitles by YayPonies\NSee you next season for more {\s1}muffins{\s0} ponies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tirek is set on{\i0}\N{\i1}possessing Alicorn magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When he comes for us, we cannot\Nhave what he is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more than willing to do\Nmy part and give up my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You misunderstand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our magic cannot just\Ndisappear into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony must keep it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That somepony is\Nyou, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not believe\Nthat Tirek is aware
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that a fourth Alicorn Princess\Nexists in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we transfer our\Nmagic to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek will not know\Nwhere it has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what\Nwe're asking of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's just I'm only now\Nlearning how to control
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,my own Alicorn magic. To\Ntake on even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you represent\Nthe Element of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is anypony who\Ncan do this, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking on this task will be one\Nof the most difficult things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But with the help\Nof my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Princess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but you must keep your\Nnew abilities a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear that your friends being\Naware of your new power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,could put them at great risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still think you can\Ntake on this responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the role I am meant to\Nplay as a Princess of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not\Nfail to do my duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must begin at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What can't be right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't gone very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean\Neverything's OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm\Ngoing back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun's not up, then\Nneither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange; the sun\Nshould be up by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun should be up by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor. Why, whatever\Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only one Discord{\i0}\N{\i1}betrayed was himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoning his true nature\Nto make "friends"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with weak-minded equines\Nwho offer him nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go and\Nhave a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand in\Nyour way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,WHERE IS YOUR MAGIC?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to gain better control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure can't practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, hi, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go...somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness. Are\Nyou all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' june bugs,\NTwilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you learn\Nto fly that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've caught a particularly\Nstrong breeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been "or something"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because there wasn't\Nany breeze up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't really have time\Nto figure it out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Another visit to the Castle of\Nthe Two Sisters, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be more than\Nhappy to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek may still be a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you all to stay here\Nand encourage everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to remain inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting rid of your magic so\Nthat I cannot take it from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that soon\Nevery Pegasus, Unicorn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and Earth Pony will\Nbow to my will
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that there is nothing\Nyou can do to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not prevail, Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to Cerberus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You meant,our will,{\i0}\N{\i1}didn't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I want you to\Nhave something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This was given to me by\Nsomeone very close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I give it to you as a sign\Nof my gratitude and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! I do love\Na good accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's\NRarity's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusing. But we have no\Ntime for such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Princesses out of\Nthe way we can now--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this meant to be humorous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't touched that one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you did not\Ntell me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just needed some assurance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that you truly considered\Nthis a team effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where can we find\Nthis fourth princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is her castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle? Oh. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight lives\Nabove a library in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle. Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, y'all,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think we've warned{\i0}\N{\i1}everypony to stay inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Discord\Nwill catch Tirek
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and this will all be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he takes\Nhis sweet time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or perhaps these things{\i0}\N{\i1}just take time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the\Ncucumber sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine they'll be your last\Ndecent meal for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gathered up all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And her little dragon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tirek offered me so much\Nmore than just tea parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you saw this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't. I really didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think she'd\Ndo anything for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If Twilight has magic to\Ngive, it will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon there won't be a Pegasus,\NEarth Pony, or Unicorn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who will be able to\Nstand up against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Us? Who said\Nanything about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've helped me grow strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've provided the means\Nby which I can obtain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you are no\Nlonger of any use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said this was a sign\Nof your gratitude and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift from someone\Nclose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother who betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is as worthless as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you saw this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't. I truly didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Ha! Perfectly\Ncontrolled teleportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PRINCESS TWILIGHT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU HAVE SOMETHING\NTHAT BELONGS TO ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to\Ngive me what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand what your\Nfellow princesses have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears we are\Nat an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a trade,\NPrincess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Their release for all the\NAlicorn magic in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it going to\Nbe, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, but you are,{\i0}\N{\i1}Fluttershy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the pony who taught\Nme that Friendship is Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had magic and friendship,\Nand now I don't have either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! I want an answer.\NAnd I want it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you my magic,\Nin exchange for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After the way he\Nhas betrayed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you still call him a "friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Release him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, what\Nwere you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek tricked me into believing\Nthat he could offer me something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,more valuable than friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is nothing worth\Nmore. I see that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He lied when he said that\Nthis medallion was given
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sign of gratitude\Nand loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I say that it is a\Nsign of our true friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that might\Nbe the last one we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get to the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have to\Ndo this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible?\NYou have no magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Tirek!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have given you\Nmy Alicorn magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I carry within me the\Nmost powerful magic of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet Celestia! Are you all\Nseeing what I'm seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But whose is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it is yours,\NPrincess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been wondering what you\Nare meant to do as a Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As Princess, I believe I\Nhave the power to spread
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Magic of Friendship{\i0}\N{\i1}across Equestria.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is the role I am meant{\i0}\N{\i1}to have in our world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The role I choose to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't defeat\NTirek on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It took all of us\Nto unlock the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it is unlikely\Nyou are meant
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to take on this\Ntask alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are now Twilight Sparkle,{\i0}\N{\i1}the Princess of Friendship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is the Princess of\NFriendship without her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.\NWhere's my throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're\Nquite there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, I suppose not.
