Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Each one of us has{\i0}\N{\i1}something special ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ That makes us different{\i0}\N{\i1}That makes us rare ♪{\i0}
